<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>Catering Inquiries — Three Wishes Bakery</title>
<meta name="description" content="Corporate and event cookie catering from nurse-owned Three Wishes Bakery, California. Trusted by hospital teams and organizations like Planned Parenthood. Weddings, showers, offices, pop-ups.">
<link rel="icon" href="../favicon.ico">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fredoka:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,600;1,600&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="../styles.css">
</head>
<body>

<div class="announce">Free nationwide shipping on orders <strong>$100+</strong> · Baked-to-order · Ships anywhere in the USA</div>

<header class="site-header">
  <nav class="nav container" aria-label="Main">
    <a class="brand" href="../index.html">
      <span class="brand-mark">✦</span>
      <span class="brand-name">Three Wishes<small>Catering</small></span>
    </a>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="../index.html#menu">Menu</a></li>
      <li><a href="../index.html#minis">Mini Packs</a></li>
      <li><a href="../index.html#sisters">Sisters</a></li>
      <li><a href="../recipes/">Recipes</a></li>
    </ul>
    <button class="cart-btn" onclick="openCart()">🛒 Cart <span data-cart-count>0</span></button>
  </nav>
</header>

<section class="page-hero container">
  <a href="../index.html" style="font-weight:700;text-decoration:none">← Back</a>
  <div style="margin-top:20px">
    <span class="eyebrow">Catering</span>
    <h1>Let's cater your <span class="serif-accent">celebration.</span></h1>
    <p>Weddings · showers · birthdays · corporate events · pop-ups. Cookie trays, sourdough boards, dessert bar spreads — built to your headcount and dietary needs. We've been the batch-bakers for our own workplaces for years — hospital teams, office celebrations, and organizations like Planned Parenthood. Tell us about your event and we'll respond within 24 hours.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section container form-wrap">
  <form onsubmit="sendCateringInquiry(event)">
    <div class="form-grid">
      <div>
        <label for="name">Full name <span class="req">*</span></label>
        <input id="name" name="name" required autocomplete="name">
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="company">Company / organization</label>
        <input id="company" name="company" autocomplete="organization">
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="email">Email <span class="req">*</span></label>
        <input id="email" name="email" type="email" required autocomplete="email">
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="phone">Phone <span class="req">*</span></label>
        <input id="phone" name="phone" type="tel" required autocomplete="tel">
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="eventType">Event type <span class="req">*</span></label>
        <select id="eventType" name="eventType" required>
          <option value="">Choose…</option>
          <option>Wedding</option>
          <option>Shower</option>
          <option>Birthday</option>
          <option>Corporate event</option>
          <option>Pop-up</option>
          <option>Other</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="eventDate">Event date <span class="req">*</span></label>
        <input id="eventDate" name="eventDate" type="date" required>
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="guests">Guest count <span class="req">*</span></label>
        <input id="guests" name="guests" type="number" min="1" required>
      </div>
      <div>
        <label for="city">Delivery city, state <span class="req">*</span></label>
        <input id="city" name="city" required>
      </div>
      <div class="full">
        <label for="details">What are you thinking? <span class="req">*</span></label>
        <textarea id="details" name="details" required placeholder="Cookie trays for 80, a sourdough board, mini boxes as favors…"></textarea>
      </div>
      <div class="full">
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" style="width:100%">Send catering inquiry</button>
        <p style="text-align:center;margin-top:14px;font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:.75rem">or email us directly · <a href="mailto:catering@3wishesbakery.com">catering@3wishesbakery.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </form>
</section>

<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="container footer-note" style="margin-top:0;border-top:none">
    <span>© 2026 Three Wishes Bakery ✦ Jeanie &amp; Patti</span>
    <span>Baked with heart in California</span>
    <span>Site crafted by <a href="https://millennialscreatives.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--rose);font-weight:700">Millennials Creatives LLC</a> ✦</span>
  </div>
</footer>

<!-- CART DRAWER -->
<div class="drawer-backdrop" onclick="closeCart()"></div>
<aside class="drawer" aria-label="Shopping cart">
  <div class="drawer-head">
    <h3>Your box · Cart (<span data-cart-count>0</span>)</h3>
    <button class="drawer-close" onclick="closeCart()" aria-label="Close cart">✕</button>
  </div>
  <div class="drawer-items" id="cartItems"></div>
  <div class="drawer-foot">
    <div class="totals"><span>Subtotal</span><span id="cartSubtotal">$0.00</span></div>
    <div class="totals"><span>Shipping</span><span id="cartShipping">—</span></div>
    <div class="totals total"><span>Total</span><span id="cartTotal">$0.00</span></div>
    <button class="checkout-btn" onclick="checkout()">Checkout</button>
    <p class="note">Free shipping on orders $100+ ✦ ships Mon &amp; Wed</p>
  </div>
</aside>

<script src="../js/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
